You can install desktop environment on Forsaken Linux

to install

For gnome doas apt install task-gnome-desktop
For kde doas apt install task-kde-desktop

after install run doas rm -rf /usr/share/desktop-base

You can also install other desktop environment

you must check ls /usr/share/desktop-base
if there is /usr/share/desktop-base run oas rm -rf /usr/share/desktop-base then doas apt-mark hold desktop-base
